Title: Sacrifices
Plot: The impending wedding of his son is the least of Teal'c's worries when the Hak'tyl plan an uprising against the Goa'uld Moloc, driving a wedge between Teal'c and Ishta.
GuestStars: Jolene Blalock, Jeff Judge, Mercedes De La Zerda, Royston Innes, Gary Jones, Simon Bailey, Noah Danby, Steve Lawlor, Dan Payne
